Luka Theme for Anchor CMS
=========================

A fully responsive theme adapted from the Greaves theme by Russell Jones

Added ZURB Orbit Slider: http://foundation.zurb.com/docs/orbit.php

Added responsive video embedding

If you're embedding video from YouTube, Vimeo, or another site that uses iframe, 
embed or object elements you can wrap your video in div.flex-video to create an 
intrinsic ratio that will properly scale your video on any device.

Added some other ZURB goodies,changed font to Exo

